response.overview: The stakes are extremely high in this wrestling program that spotlights an exciting championship battle between two of the XPW's biggest names: Sabu and Messiah. If Sabu fails to capture the championship title, he must quit the XPW forever. Also included are several other thrilling matches, including an eight-man tournament and a brutal, unforgettable battle royal that features Pogo the Clown and Major Gunns.
response.title: XPW: Damage, Inc.
